laboratory_examinations.findings: Trace aortic regurgitation and a mean gradient of 8 mm Hg. Estimated aortic orifice area is 2.1 cm² (indexed orifice area: 1.3 cm²/m²). Left ventricular end-diastolic and end-systolic diameters are 46 and 30 mm, respectively. Left ventricular ejection fraction is preserved.
